original_title: Sri Lanka coconut auction prices rise 7.79-pct
original_body_lines: ECONOMYNEXT- Sri Lanka’s average coconut prices were up from 93,865.10 to 101,177.51 for 1,000 nuts at an auction on October 10, data from the Coconut Development Authority shows.
The highest price was 115,000 for 1,000 nuts while the lowest was 85,900.
A total of 568,859 coconuts were offered at the auction and 532,346 were sold.
